<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA621_05_SU_0003_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    
    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />
    
    <!-- 개별 -->
    <script src="../../common_contents/js/ema621_05_0003.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema621_05.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema621_05_su_0003">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1" lang="y">
          <div class="fraction_row">
            <div class="fraction_inn">
              아라온호가 일정한 빠르기로 6 ㎞를 가는 데
              <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>3</span></span>시간이 걸렸습니다. 아라온호가 같은 빠르기로 1시간 동안 몇 ㎞를 갈 수 있는지
            </div>
            알아봅시다.
          </div>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
            <article class="page page_1">
              <div class="img_row">
                <div class="picture_wrap type2">
                <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA621_05_SU/0003_content.png" alt="" />
                  <button class="zoom"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="input_area">
                  <h3 lang="y">6 ㎞를 가는 데 2시간이 걸렸다면 1시간 동안 몇 ㎞를 갔나요?</h3>
                  <div class="question_box justify_center">
                    <div class="col">
                      <span class="f32b">6÷2=</span>
                      <div class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="up">
                        <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                      </div>
                      <span class="f32b">이므로 1시간 동안</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col">
                      <div class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                      </div>
                      <span class="f32b">㎞를 갔습니다.</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_2">
              <div class="img_row">
                <div class="picture_wrap type2">
                <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA621_05_SU/0003_content.png" alt="" />
                  <button class="zoom"></button>
                </div>
              <div class="input_area">
                <h3 lang="y">
                  <div class="fraction_row">
                    <div class="fraction_inn">
                      6 ㎞를 가는 데 <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>3</span></span> 시간이 걸렸다면1시간 동안 몇 ㎞를
                    </div>
                     갈 수 있는지 구하는 식을 써 보세요.
                  </div>
                </h3>
                <div class="question_box justify_center">
                  <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="6-:(2)/(3)"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_3">
              <h3 lang="y">
                위에서 구한 식을 어떻게 계산할 수 있는지 생각해 보고, 그림을 이용하여 알아보세요.
              </h3>
              
              <div class="question_box">
                  <div class="col1">
                      <div class="txt txt1">6 ㎞</div>  
                      <div class="txt txt2">0</div>  
                      <div class="txt txt3">
                        <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>3</span></span>
                      </div>  
                      <div class="txt txt4">
                        <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>3</span></span>
                      </div>  
                      <div class="txt txt5">1</div>  
                      <div class="txt txt6">(시간)</div>
                      <div class="speech_bubble">
                        <div class="bubble_txt">
                          <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>3</span></span>
                          시간은&nbsp;
                          <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>3</span></span>
                          시간을 2로 나눈 것과 같아.
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col_txt6">&divide;2</div>
                      <button type="button" class="btn_arr arr_btn1"><i>선택</i></button>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col2">
                    
                      <div class="txt txt1">3 ㎞</div>  
                      <div class="txt txt2">0</div>  
                      <div class="txt txt3">
                        <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>3</span></span>
                      </div>  
                      <div class="txt txt4">
                        <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>3</span></span>
                      </div>  
                      <div class="txt txt5">1</div>  
                      <div class="txt txt6">(시간)</div>
                      <div class="speech_bubble">
                        <div class="bubble_txt">
                          1시간은&nbsp;
                          <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>3</span></span>
                          시간을 3배 한 것과 같아.
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col_txt6">&times;3</div>
                      <button type="button" class="btn_arr arr_btn2"><i>선택</i></button>
                  </div>
                   <div class="col3">
                    
                      <div class="txt txt1">3 ㎞</div>  
                      <div class="txt txt1_2">3 ㎞</div>  
                      <div class="txt txt1_3">3 ㎞</div>  
                      <div class="txt txt2">0</div>
                      <div class="txt txt3">
                        <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>3</span></span>
                      </div>  
                      <div class="txt txt4">
                        <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>3</span></span>
                      </div>  
                      <div class="txt txt5">1</div>  
                      <div class="txt txt6">(시간)</div>
                    </div>
                
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_4">
              <div class="img_row">
                <div class="picture_wrap type2">
                <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA621_05_SU/0003_content.png" alt="" />
                  <button class="zoom"></button>
                </div>
              <div class="input_area">
                <h3 lang="y">
                  <div class="fraction_row">
                    <div class="fraction_inn">
                      6 ㎞를 가는 데 <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>3</span></span> 시간이 걸렸다면 1시간 동안 몇 ㎞를
                    </div>
                    갈 수 있는지 구하는 식을 써 보세요.
                  </div>
                </h3>
                <div class="question_box justify_center">
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="6"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  <span class="f32b">배</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>
            
            

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <!-- <button class="btnSubmit">확인</button> -->
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
